      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis index comparison against experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal pump at five flow-speed operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty bounds. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all operating points."
    },
