      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation and GCI analysis performed across three mesh levels. GCI for NIH < 2.1% on the medium mesh. Wall y+ maintained below 1 on impeller blade surfaces to resolve shear-dominated hemolysis source terms."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
