      "rationale": "In-vitro test loop operated at 37°C with bovine blood at 30% hematocrit. Flow rates and rotational speeds measured with calibrated Coriolis meter and optical encoder respectively. Uncertainty in boundary conditions quantified and propagated to simulation inputs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
