      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal test sample characterization beyond the documented lot information is not required at MRL 2. Bovine blood lots used in validation testing were documented with hematocrit and plasma hemoglobin baseline measurements."
